// conflict/project.das_project — Tests module name collision detection
//
// Uses the default resolver from common.das_project which maps
// `require pkgA/foo` to moduleName "foo" (last path component) and
// `require pkgB/foo` to moduleName "foo" — same module name, different files.
//
// The compiler should detect this and fail.

options gen2
require strings
require daslib/strings_boost

include ../common.das_project
